video_title: Next time you’re stressed, try this ❤️ #shorts
transcript:
if you ever feel like your mind is ahead
or your body's behind or your body's
ahead or your mind's behind simply
breathe in for the same amount of time
as you breathe out and you can count the
numbers in your head and you'll see that
your body and mind slowly
start to respond to each other and your
body will actually calm down
